{"tid":1886330,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"買木結他2020","createTime":"2020-02-18T23:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T20:15:33.000Z","uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e682953152b0d2f52714aec718e0e6388c0d48f8","tid":1886330,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:05:05.000Z","msg":"新手學咗半年，以家用個支係F310想換過把新，原因係覺得呢排練結他比之前勤力咗，所以想keep住日日都練買個把新結他比動力自己，第二，彈過我啊sir個支taylor覺得好好禁好揸同好聽，但係太貴，budget 2xxx 唔買2手有潔癖，唔一定要大牌子，想要單板，上網睇過veelah V1D 好似唔錯，但係通利同柏G都冇 或者推薦一啲牌子比我 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e494c59603cd9d202e6096a28f200279f5d56664","tid":1886330,"uid":132690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:08:22.000Z","msg":"你sir支Taylor 係咩model?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8893a18a004510795775ed24ca669c211ed57546","tid":1886330,"uid":252937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:27:18.000Z","msg":"Budget 2千幾玩番F310算啦，因為根本唔差。"},{"pid":"a47ccec47d70dfff48c58666271f767d0245196f","tid":1886330,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e494c59603cd9d202e6096a28f200279f5d56664","tid":1886330,"uid":132690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:08:22.000Z","msg":"你sir支Taylor 係咩model?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"唔知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e298fafe90684769010cb2190f2441e4a89818","tid":1886330,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8893a18a004510795775ed24ca669c211ed57546","tid":1886330,"uid":252937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:27:18.000Z","msg":"Budget 2千幾玩番F310算啦，因為根本唔差。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"好啦咁再諗下先，師兄有冇咩牌子好，等我研究下"},{"pid":"ce971967e941899fc9a08ef9398690d6e8735f21","tid":1886330,"uid":252937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c2e298fafe90684769010cb2190f2441e4a89818","tid":1886330,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8893a18a004510795775ed24ca669c211ed57546","tid":1886330,"uid":252937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:27:18.000Z","msg":"Budget 2千幾玩番F310算啦，因為根本唔差。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"好啦咁再諗下先，師兄有冇咩牌子好，等我研究下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"初學結他，牌子真唔緊要。硬要推的，就是你手上的F310，夠玩十年以上，就算之後入咗支靚野，留返低粗用都抵（我自己支F3唔記得咩都陪了我近三十年仲彈緊，不過當年用料係好過而家嘅）<br />\n<br />\n你現在最重要係有支唔駛𡃶身隨時隨地粗玩既結他，增加練習時間。無謂花錢跟我哩庭3唔識7口水佬既口碑去買，第日自己真係識既時候一定後悔。與其係咁不如儲多啲錢一買就買支真係好既（目標可以係二萬樓下左右），到時就真係有支威得起既好野，唔會嘥錢買中間過渡物。<br />\n<br />\n睇吓Yamaha都可以玩fingerstyle,有好嘢就唔好浪費<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kw9jOdmC_70\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKw9jOdmC_70&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=86e58dc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kw9jOdmC_70</a><br />\n<br />\n加油努力啦！"},{"pid":"7074caf032ad3c75cb13ec1bc428d5ab953cdfbe","tid":1886330,"uid":197350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e682953152b0d2f52714aec718e0e6388c0d48f8","tid":1886330,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:05:05.000Z","msg":"新手學咗半年，以家用個支係F310想換過把新，原因係覺得呢排練結他比之前勤力咗，所以想keep住日日都練買個把新結他比動力自己，第二，彈過我啊sir個支taylor覺得好好禁好揸同好聽，但係太貴，budget 2xxx 唔買2手有潔癖，唔一定要大牌子，想要單板，上網睇過veelah V1D 好似唔錯，但係通利同柏G都冇 或者推薦一啲牌子比我 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"兩樣野，<br />\n 一， 好禁唔關支結他事， 係setting問題同線老化問題， 自己學下點set支f310仲好<br />\n二， 1000蚊f310上2000蚊結他真係不如用返f310, 再慢慢儲錢買貴小小。 如果要上taylor100系列， 我會覺得買同價yamaha更好<br />\n<br />\n利申: 用緊taylor 114ce"},{"pid":"af00663626eed564f5c9b4c8f9a38672e01d6